    <item>
      <title>印度财政部长预计人均收入将几乎翻一番</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-s-finance-minister-sees-per-capita-income-almost-doubling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部长尼尔玛拉·西塔拉曼表示，随着经济持续增长，五年内人均收入将几乎翻一番，同时警告称，目前的全球环境比过去更加严峻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-s-finance-minister-sees-per-capita-income-almost-doubling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称现代汽车将在印度最大规模 IPO 中寻求 190 亿美元的估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hyundai-is-said-to-seek-19-billion-value-in-india-s-biggest-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，现代汽车公司希望其印度子公司首次公开募股的估值为 190 亿美元，这可能是印度规模最大的股票发行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hyundai-is-said-to-seek-19-billion-value-in-india-s-biggest-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 10:08:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
