      <title>全球银行纷纷呼吁土耳其降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/global-banks-rush-to-recast-calls-for-turkish-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于土耳其九月份通胀数据高于预期，华尔街银行不得不重新制定其对土耳其首次降息时间的预测。]]></description>
