      <title>欧盟将对中国电动汽车征收最高达 45% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-votes-to-impose-tariffs-of-up-to-45-on-china-made-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周五投票决定对中国生产的电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税，此举将加剧与北京的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-votes-to-impose-tariffs-of-up-to-45-on-china-made-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
